@startuml 4A_Product_Management
title 4-A · Merch Product Management (UC-T27 to UC-T29)

start
|Tenant Admin (Owner/Admin)|
:Open Merch > New Product;

|System|
:Verify tenant status = ACTIVE;
:Check plan includes merchandise feature;
if (Merch feature allowed?) then (No)
  :Return 403 with upgrade prompt;
  stop
else (Yes)
  |Tenant Admin (Owner/Admin)|
  :Enter product name, description,\nbase price, currency and category;
  :Upload cover/gallery images;
  :Add one or more variants\n(SKU, price, stock, attributes);
endif

|System|
:Validate required fields and unique SKUs;
if (Validation passed?) then (No)
  :Return 422 with field/SKU errors;
  stop
else (Yes)
  :Create MerchProduct status = DRAFT;
  :Create MerchVariant records;
endif

|Tenant Admin (Owner/Admin)|
if (Admin action?) then (Publish)
  |System|
  :Set product status = ACTIVE;
  :Product appears in Merch Store;
elseif (Admin action?) then (Update Stock)
  :Enter stock changes per variant;
  |System|
  :Update stock levels;
  if (Stock available?) then (Yes)
    :Keep product purchasable;
  else (No)
    :Show out-of-stock state to fans;
  endif
else (Keep Draft)
  |System|
  :Product remains hidden from fans;
endif

stop
@enduml
